    {
      "segment_id": "cf898102",
      "source_content": "This document describes how to start Chaos Mesh quickly in a test or local environment.",
      "source_content_hash": "9226c304cf8a9eeaf594094b054bffba8c4840dff287a013402a5231deef1107",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "このドキュメントでは、テスト環境やローカル環境でChaos Meshを迅速に開始する方法について説明します。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "a7378c68",
      "source_content": ":::caution\n\n**In this document, Chaos Mesh is installed via a script for quick trial only.**\n\nIf you need to install Chaos Mesh in the production environment or other strict non-test scenarios, it is recommended to use [Helm](https://helm.sh/). For more details, refer to [Installation using Helm](production-installation-using-helm.md).\n\n:::",
      "source_content_hash": "82547a63c04f84317cf02826f85aa9532f8626227d3e3595319fe4b3ce3f269a",
      "node_type": "containerDirective",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": ":::caution\n\n**このドキュメントでは、Chaos Meshはクイックトライアルのためスクリプト経由でインストールされます。**\n\n本番環境やその他の厳格な非テストシナリオでChaos Meshをインストールする必要がある場合は、[Helm](https://helm.sh/)を使用することを推奨します。詳細については、[Helmを使用したインストール](production-installation-using-helm.md)を参照してください。\n\n:::"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "ed7dde9c",
      "source_content": "## Environment preparation",
      "source_content_hash": "e5f5bb1c4a07acdb4d72895ce64eb75416847741ef4095e5a8d4b201a92302a4",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "## 環境の準備"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "a76548f8",
      "source_content": "Please ensure that the Kubernetes cluster is deployed in the environment before the trial. If the Kubernetes cluster has not been deployed, you can refer to the links below to complete the deployment:",
      "source_content_hash": "1bd84b390f27fd53cf7b215776ab3db2c9d6546c77e16e1397ec99e0ed649d27",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "トライアル前に、環境にKubernetesクラスターがデプロイされていることを確認してください。Kubernetesクラスターがまだデプロイされていない場合は、以下のリンクを参照してデプロイを完了してください："
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "77bf3ec9",
      "source_content": "- [Kubernetes](https://kubernetes.io/docs/setup/)\n- [minikube](https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/start/)\n- [kind](https://kind.sigs.k8s.io/docs/user/quick-start/)\n- [K3s](https://rancher.com/docs/k3s/latest/en/quick-start/)\n- [Microk8s](https://microk8s.io/)",
      "source_content_hash": "828065951a495c148422fa521152c7aadb299dc8e78f6186231bfc11dcec3d39",
      "node_type": "list",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "- [Kubernetes](https://kubernetes.io/docs/setup/)\n- [minikube](https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/start/)\n- [kind](https://kind.sigs.k8s.io/docs/user/quick-start/)\n- [K3s](https://rancher.com/docs/k3s/latest/en/quick-start/)\n- [Microk8s](https://microk8s.io/)"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "f422383e",
      "source_content": "## Quick installation",
      "source_content_hash": "ca4312ff790afaec31a0fe346bb31ce20071c32ef902492b3242f4595b0f8f16",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "## クイックインストール"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "97ae4a01",
      "source_content": "To install Chaos Mesh in a test environment, run the following script:",
      "source_content_hash": "da3d074f9677d6be1447a1f5c234040e71c8460d437595bb3d99a7e4a4aea99e",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "テスト環境でChaos Meshをインストールするには、以下のスクリプトを実行します："
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "28e10980",
      "source_content": "<!-- prettier-ignore -->",
      "source_content_hash": "a94eeea12154992988ea88567eed85506a35d1f83e439a912e23fafd65191f47",
      "node_type": "comment",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_28e10980"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "1641af73",
      "source_content": "<Tabs defaultValue=\"k8s\" values={[\n  {label: 'K8s', value: 'k8s'},\n  {label: 'kind', value: 'kind'},\n  {label: 'K3s', value: 'k3s'},\n  {label: 'MicroK8s', value: 'microk8s'}\n]}>\n  <TabItem value=\"k8s\">\n    <PickVersion>\n    {`curl -sSL https://mirrors.chaos-mesh.org/latest/install.sh | bash`}\n    </PickVersion>\n  </TabItem>\n  <TabItem value=\"kind\">\n    <PickVersion>{`curl -sSL https://mirrors.chaos-mesh.org/latest/install.sh | bash -s -- --local kind`}</PickVersion>\n\n    If you want to specify a `kind` version, add the `--kind-version xx` parameter at the end of the script, for example:\n\n    <PickVersion>\n    {`curl -sSL https://mirrors.chaos-mesh.org/latest/install.sh | bash -s -- --local kind --kind-version v0.20.0`}\n    </PickVersion>\n\n  </TabItem>\n  <TabItem value=\"k3s\">\n    <PickVersion>\n    {`curl -sSL https://mirrors.chaos-mesh.org/latest/install.sh | bash -s -- --k3s`}\n    </PickVersion>\n  </TabItem>\n  <TabItem value=\"microk8s\">\n    <PickVersion>\n    {`curl -sSL https://mirrors.chaos-mesh.org/latest/install.sh | bash -s -- --microk8s`}\n    </PickVersion>\n  </TabItem>\n</Tabs>",
      "source_content_hash": "a31240841302552e4c581fc59c94a2267947f295458c1b56ccd0427912f1ce73",
      "node_type": "mdxJsxFlowElement",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_1641af73"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "eab056be",
      "source_content": "After running, Chaos Mesh will automatically install the appropriate version of CustomResourceDefinitions and the required components.",
      "source_content_hash": "a75493b5fca3be279060f69bf535a40307e44eac5d662dffa8985f153b7977db",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "実行後、Chaos Meshは適切なバージョンのCustomResourceDefinitionsと必要なコンポーネントを自動的にインストールします。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "f01228d3",
      "source_content": "For more installation details, refer to the source code of the [`install.sh`](https://github.com/chaos-mesh/chaos-mesh/blob/master/install.sh).",
      "source_content_hash": "0fb34d07f57fc65db37c19611d09e7ec714acbe7f9d780f67bb0bb4fcea11ace",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "インストールの詳細については、[`install.sh`](https://github.com/chaos-mesh/chaos-mesh/blob/master/install.sh)のソースコードを参照してください。"
      }
    },
    {
