    {
      "segment_id": "0a103a02",
      "source_content": "## Uninstall Chaos Mesh",
      "source_content_hash": "ab80d8b7494f870b8fc95c1724720f1abc9e343d7de90d1758433f83418c2bb6",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "## Chaos Meshのアンインストール"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "8126f763",
      "source_content": "To uninstall Chaos Mesh, execute the following command:",
      "source_content_hash": "5f34dc8c1d90d6968703a678bcd3e0b49211ebb9cc10fd684eac3df252a3378f",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "Chaos Meshをアンインストールするには、以下のコマンドを実行します："
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "897e0025",
      "source_content": "<PickVersion>\n{`curl -sSL https://mirrors.chaos-mesh.org/latest/install.sh | bash -s -- --template | kubectl delete -f -`}\n</PickVersion>",
      "source_content_hash": "2195cc2c39d6c9727be14dc1db90159566fe50de9ee32e5cf091f8fda2c4ac99",
      "node_type": "mdxJsxFlowElement",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_897e0025"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "51867d16",
      "source_content": "You can also delete the `chaos-mesh` namespace to directly uninstall Chaos Mesh:",
      "source_content_hash": "dbe2860d9c2714a5b356c1bbde0c045bad3433ce6059a68df01a310da1e68113",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "また、`chaos-mesh`ネームスペースを削除することで直接Chaos Meshをアンインストールすることもできます："
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "59f28e14",
      "source_content": "```sh\nkubectl delete ns chaos-mesh\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "a8b21828d0291a7daff067d83ee2183b78a33d8c62c2148940c967ea6e9b60c4",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_59f28e14"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "e06c002e",
      "source_content": "## FAQ",
      "source_content_hash": "b07ed55203f0d88ebed77a69ea750333f4f62ec38193b32272aa2987376f7b86",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "## FAQ"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "99d0dd9b",
      "source_content": "### Why the `local` directory appears in the root directory after installation?",
      "source_content_hash": "94397d2d6fa044e779a36ae0e0bbd6ecaf1cea195c1db7a030eb461d4a0d1f6b",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "### インストール後にルートディレクトリに`local`ディレクトリが表示されるのはなぜですか？"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "d79a4831",
      "source_content": "If you don't install `kind` in the existing environment, and you use the `--local kind` parameter when executing the installation command, the `install.sh` script will automatically install the `kind` in the `local` directory under the root directory.",
      "source_content_hash": "af2ac7a5e06bd5aabd37bc2fbc824eb35446d89629033a5c731c2f0e1a1c0354",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "既存の環境に`kind`がインストールされておらず、インストールコマンドを実行する際に`--local kind`パラメータを使用した場合、`install.sh`スクリプトはルートディレクトリの`local`ディレクトリに`kind`を自動的にインストールします。"
      }
    }
